title: futurama seasons 1-5 RMVB [revival]
description:
This is a convert from .avi files to smaller size yet still surprisingly good quality at 640x480. I got it off megaupload while looking for a complete futurama pack with acceptable size/quality. 

Honestly, I thought a 200mb .avi was a bit much per 30min cartoon episode as it&#039;s what&#039;s available out there atm (anything less is shitty video or tiny resolution), so this rmvb format is something of a compromise.

Seeding: ummm, I don&#039;t have unlimited resources here, but I&#039;ll hang in there, in the long run it&#039;s up to DHT...
